{"tid":1560980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲藍絲成日都好多問題問，決定整合一啲常見問題比大家睇下","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:34:06.000Z","uid":1477,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b69aceabb6a62380785655e854d361c44aac31","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"當中可能有d 答案答得唔太好，甚至係差，麻煩各位幫手改良下，不勝感激！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\nQ1: 點解要出黎搞事？<br />\nA1: 因為香港特區政府提出修訂逃犯條例，香港各界人士表示反對有關修訂，但政府卻未有理會，因此各界別人士以及市民發起遊行示威，包括6月9日103萬人遊行以發6月16日200萬+1人遊行。唯政府堅持立場，未有撤回有關修訂草案，故自6月9日以來，示威行動持續。<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 你地爭取嘅五大訴求係咩黎？<br />\nA2: 撤回議案，取消暴動定性，釋放被捕人士，調查警隊濫權濫暴，實行雙普選。<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 點解你地要著黑衫，戴口罩，唔比人地見到你個樣？<br />\nA3: 因為政府及警隊濫權，2019年的夏季，遊行示威已被視為反政府行動，Black Bloc 是為了避免被警方紀錄樣貌，日後秋後算帳。 而事實上已有多名政治人物，包括議員已被警方無理拘捕。<br />\n<br />\nQ4: 其實你地出黎一次收幾多錢？<br />\nA4: 本人絕無收取一分一毫，相反購買物資已花費不少金錢。<br />\n<br />\nQ5: 你地背後嘅大台係邊個？<br />\nA5: 純由民間自發，並無領袖主導今次嘅社會運動。<br />\n<br />\nQ6: 點解你地要佔路？<br />\nA6: 我們希望政府能正視我們的決心，佔路是為了逼使政府正面回應我方訴求，而不是逃避。<br />\n<br />\nQ7: 點解你地要拆野，整路障？<br />\nA7: 因為警隊濫捕，建立路障只是為了使示威者與警察中間出現防線，一旦警方快速推進，示威者亦可借路障爭取時間撤到安全位置。<br />\n<br />\nQ8: 點解你地要阻住警察做野？<br />\nA8: 我們的行動是為了逼使政府回應訴求，而不是渴望警隊的鎮壓，尢其是警察於清場時面對手無寸鐵的示威者採用過度武力。但示威者並無意與警方為敵，只是警方視示威者如仇敵。<br />\n<br />\nQ9: 點解你地要襲警？<br />\nA9: 我們的裝備是為了抵擋警察無止境的警暴，而不是主動襲警，警方無理濫暴在先，以至令抗爭者迫於無奈下為保護自己而還擊，但焦點從不在警方。<br />\n<br />\nQ10: 點解你地要包圍警署？<br />\nA10: 因為警方濫捕﹑濫暴。警察於近三個月多次無理拘捕市民，示威者前往警署並非包圍警察，只是聲援被捕人士，希望警方盡快釋放無辜市民。<br />\n<br />\nQ11: 點解你地要阻住地鐵運作？<br />\nA11: 我們希望此行動能逼使政府回應訴求，而非逃避。<br />\n<br />\nQ12: 點解你地要阻住人搵食？<br />\nA12: 我們的焦點是政府，不是人民，我們只希望盡力喚醒市民，使他們能夠知道政府的惡行。<br />\n<br />\nQ13: 點解唔靜靜地和平集會，係都要影響到人？<br />\nA13: 因為政府無視我們的和平集會及遊行，是政府教我們，和平是沒有任何作用。<br />\n<br />\nQ14: 點解要痴連儂牆？<br />\nA14: 希望透過和理非的方式，向同路人打氣加油。以及希望透過連儂牆傳送資訊給各界人士。<br />\n<br />\nQ15: 點解每晚10點都要鳩叫？<br />\nA15: 希望大家能夠透過聲音來確認身邊有戰友，知道自己不是孤單的，明白身邊仍然有人在堅持。<br />\n<br />\nQ16: 點解要拆地鐵站嘅設施？<br />\nA16: 運動伊始，儘管人數多寡，市民都守秩序排隊買票候車，從不鼓躁，甚至於售票機留下零錢，讓學生買票，表現出文明社會的應有典範。<br />\n可惜由７２１、８３１等事件，看出港鐵並不是站在乘客一方，未能做好保護乘客的職責，港鐵的行為使乘客身陷危險之中，卻不施以援手。拆港鐵站設施，一方面爭取時間讓市民走避。另一方面，在不傷及職員情況下表達不滿、痛心疾首。我們相信設施壞了可以重建，但對港鐵的信任已不復來。<br />\n<br />\nQ17: 點解要去機場和你飛？<br />\nA17: 希望能夠使外國旅客留意到我們的訴求，幫忙向國際表達香港的困局。<br />\n<br />\nQ18: 點解要手拖手做人鏈？<br />\nA18: 希望用和理非嘅方法，證明我地係會願意用和理非嘅行動黎爭取訴求。<br />\n<br />\nQ19: 點解你地要香港獨立？<br />\nA19: 我們不是港獨。<br />\n<br />\nQ20: 到底你地幾時先肯停？<br />\nA20: 光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n講得唔好請唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我亦唔係想代表任何人，只係有時見到有人會面對呢d 問題口啞啞，覺得咁樣輸左道氣好唔抵，如果大家覺得咁樣係唔岩，我會請求連仔del post.<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港 Glory To HongKong</span></span>"},{"pid":"4d57f6304acb8f0728aa8eb6da3a1e2e8e7e3a59","tid":1560980,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c77c80f72f25f6b89b34655096cebecd5a52eba1","tid":1560980,"uid":189377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"算啦 你覺得啲藍絲會聽你講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae1df80103cdcd540c21cbd73b7809796b6a603","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c77c80f72f25f6b89b34655096cebecd5a52eba1","tid":1560980,"uid":189377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"算啦 你覺得啲藍絲會聽你講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"無所謂嘅我覺得，一黎可以比自己人睇下，有時聽到d 問題，自己都會呆左呆先諗到點答"},{"pid":"e8db9b83a962152849fccaaadcf01bdbdea08eee","tid":1560980,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"教材post"},{"pid":"91a268dba2a4d2e08601ee0002b218e72baec7c1","tid":1560980,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"民主可以當飯食咩？<br />\n點答好？"},{"pid":"282a3bb16061df410d26e191d77165f4537862c6","tid":1560980,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"Q: 知唔知而家無遊客嚟香港，好多人每無工開？"},{"pid":"7c6d242e21bdaac4fb4fcb8161a1be0ed27978ca","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91a268dba2a4d2e08601ee0002b218e72baec7c1","tid":1560980,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"民主可以當飯食咩？<br />\n點答好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"民主唔可以當飯食，但係如果無民主，你就算煮好一枱滿漢全席，你諗住起筷果陣，佢都可以趕你走，然後搵埋自己嘅朋友食。"},{"pid":"fcaf7dd5b7ab586613ec18a245c7137d2c482df1","tid":1560980,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"282a3bb16061df410d26e191d77165f4537862c6","tid":1560980,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"Q: 知唔知而家無遊客嚟香港，好多人每無工開？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"旅遊業從來不應只注重搵快錢及只吸引單一客源<br />\n<br />\n之前賺唔夠咩？"},{"pid":"1e5212018493ac5cae8db5b911151d60a977d081","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"282a3bb16061df410d26e191d77165f4537862c6","tid":1560980,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"Q: 知唔知而家無遊客嚟香港，好多人每無工開？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7px3F4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7px3F4.jpg&h=c0034080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係事實，旅遊業其實只係佔好少數。<br />\n另外，高消費力嘅中国人始終會繼續黎香港，因為最平最方便，少左嘅其實係水貨客為主，條路少左人，少左藥房，其實係好事。<br />\n事實上香港而家嘅發展已經有d 畸形，而家可以重新諗下發展方向。"},{"pid":"9255b4f2a17eef715d52bd9cfef8104eb2a5c1cb","tid":1560980,"uid":273708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"有冇呢類嘅QNA文宣？貼牆唔錯"},{"pid":"cebc5137650a13492dbd4b2145f0f9f9a481cf9a","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9255b4f2a17eef715d52bd9cfef8104eb2a5c1cb","tid":1560980,"uid":273708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"有冇呢類嘅QNA文宣？貼牆唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己早幾日諗到嘅，今日先得閒寫"},{"pid":"0d051a0eb09c050bf4b9b43430afe181e03348e6","tid":1560980,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得大部問題可以直接答<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadcfa8f75c6ee81ea7a903a672a124271fe8d04","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d051a0eb09c050bf4b9b43430afe181e03348e6","tid":1560980,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得大部問題可以直接答<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"但其實咁樣唔太好，我相信有d 問題就算係深黃可能都要諗一諗先答到"},{"pid":"7cf4ae838f143da6e6a8f937de10bebdcf874922","tid":1560980,"uid":118176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d72004690a91deffa15b8f32f7fe36713b6ed01f","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cf4ae838f143da6e6a8f937de10bebdcf874922","tid":1560980,"uid":118176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:33:43.000Z","msg":"當然啦 只係希望大家面前呢d 問題可以即刻up 到答案出黎 唔係口啞啞 erererer"},{"pid":"3465784742c4b10c10248d854302b69009f3584c","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34d6931015bd47fa3b748313581c7d41edade66","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef445c061a289aea4a5792b15a3e93cdd231334","tid":1560980,"uid":272608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:14:09.000Z","msg":"問好成日話冇用,,,藍絲都係香港人...<br />\n雖然話人一藍,腦就殘.<br />\n但你想比人知道你腦正常都要識答呢類問題!<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aea79724e9b8a0995726228853fc3eb197983e","tid":1560980,"uid":272608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:14:30.000Z","msg":"樓主有心,幫推幾個"},{"pid":"dae9c17c70b5090069cec0a9607f5cfa9cbd3325","tid":1560980,"uid":272608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8013042063e5cea0975c75f64d747a024331e65b","tid":1560980,"uid":272608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"和理非應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324b9b19810c8650e0aaae39cd2b95ebf219977d","tid":1560980,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:20:13.000Z","msg":"Q1唔update喎, 佢又真係聲稱撤回左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ1.1 點解撤回左仲搞事?<br />\nA1.1 五大訴求, 缺一不可"},{"pid":"d99319ea061856d72b07d4b5471c17ab890f6cd2","tid":1560980,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"324b9b19810c8650e0aaae39cd2b95ebf219977d","tid":1560980,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:20:13.000Z","msg":"Q1唔update喎, 佢又真係聲稱撤回左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ1.1 點解撤回左仲搞事?<br />\nA1.1 五大訴求, 缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢樣野反映香港真係好大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cedb7327dfc93af9eb48683210733a3571f42d","tid":1560980,"uid":308822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"P牌都幫推，高質post!"}]}